messages.message: I'm noticing a lot of timeouts in our CI builds - is our Cypress environment slow right now?

in runs from earlier this morning, it seems that `job-service` was still unhealthy

ex: digitization jobs could not be started at around 7am PT bc of the same error from yesterday

however, job-service (https://crafting-cyp.test.instabase.com/deployment-manager/dashboard/deployments/apps/v1/job-service) seems to be healthy now

and jobs are running successfully (see screenshot of some successfully created projects from some CI run)
Hm, could it be that job-service is being hit with a backlog of jobs that were created back when it wasn't healthy, thus taking a long time and therefore causing timeouts?
yes, that could definitely be related :disappointed:
